Yohan Bilingi (a mụrụ ya n'ụbọchị nke 1 mbụ n'ọnwa Febụwarị n'afọ 1999) bụ onye France na-agba bọọlụ nke na-agbachitere Ligue 2 club En Avant Guingamp
Bilingi bụbu onye egwuregwu ụlọ akwụkwọ ndị ntorobịa nke Cannes

Mgbe ọ gụsịrị akwụkwọ na ụlọ akwụkwọ Guingamp, o sonyeere Bastia-Borgo na mgbazinye ego n'ọnwa Septemba n'afọ 2019. Na 31 Mee 2020, Concarneau kwupụtara ntinye aka nke Bilingi na nkwekọrịta mgbazinye ego ogologo oge.
Mgbe ọ laghachiri Guingamp mgbe ọ gbazinyere ego ugboro abụọ n'usoro, Bilingi mere egwuregwu izizi ya na 24 Julaị 2021 na goolu na Le Havre.
Bilingi bụbu onye otu egwuregwu mba ndị ntorobịa France
Ọ gbara egwuregwu abụọ maka ndị na-erubeghị afọ iri na itoolu n'afọ 2017.
